{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel1 \b \fs32 7. The decision points (review these at month 3, 6, 12)\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 {\b Month 3 review (after launch):}\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Did the launch produce \u8805 ? \u8364 ?15k revenue (lifetime burst + first licences)? If yes, double down on Bucket B. If no, the positioning is wrong \u8212- pivot to one of the other decks ({\f1 agency}, {\f1 hotel}, {\f1 doctor}, {\f1 softwarestore}).\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Did Elest.io listing go live and attract \u8805 ? 5 deploys? If no, the listing copy or the deploy template needs work.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Discord size \u8805 ? 100 members? If no, the launch didn't reach the right audience.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Operator Cookbook sold \u8805 ? 20 units? If no, either the price is wrong or the cookbook isn't being surfaced on the right pages.\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 {\b Month 6 review:}\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab MRR equivalent (priority-support add-on + Elest.io rev-share + plugin marketplace + licence renewals coming due) \u8805 ? \u8364 ?1,500? If no, the recurring base isn't compounding \u8212- adjust pricing or tiers.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Cumulative revenue \u8805 ? \u8364 ?40k? On track for \u8364 ?100k.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Any plugin in the marketplace earning \u8805 ? \u8364 ?500/mo? If no, the marketplace isn't taking off \u8212- recruit 2\u8211-3 specific plugin authors directly (async DM, no call) or shelve the line.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Are \u8805 ? 3 customers asking for managed hosting? If yes, {\b start the white-label hosting-partner search} (Path C from the chat) \u8212- sign one by end of Y1.\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 {\b Month 12 review:}\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Did you hit \u8364 ?100k? If yes, the model works \u8212- go to Y2 and add the agency channel (Bucket C) by hiring a part-time SDR or signing 1\u8211-2 reseller deals.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab If \u8364 ?60\u8211-\u8364 ?100k: model works but slower. Stay solo, repeat Y1 playbook with Y1's audience as launch fuel.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab If < \u8364 ?60k: the constraint (10 hrs/week + no sync) is incompatible with the target. Either increase hours, or accept a longer trajectory.\sa180\par}
